
station-event-bluespace-dungeon-start-announcement = Attention! VMSRM reports a high entropy object breaching realspace near the Arion.
station-event-bluespace-dungeon-warning-announcement = Attention! The VMSRM is reporting an increasing subspace wake. ETA T minus five minutes until unidentified object subspace bubble destabilization.
station-event-bluespace-dungeon-end-announcement = Attention! VMSRM reports that the high entropy object has destabilized and exited realspace.

station-event-bluespace-scrap-start-announcement = Attention! VMSRM reports subspace storms revealing ship wreckage near the Arion.
station-event-bluespace-scrap-warning-announcement = Attention! The subspace storm is waning. ETA T minus five minutes until the wreckage exits realspace.
station-event-bluespace-scrap-end-announcement = Attention! The subspace storm has passed, and the ship wreckage has exited realspace.

